top -p <pid>
top -i: 不显示闲置或者僵尸进程
top -c: 显示整个命令行而不是仅仅显示命令名


? or h: help information
k: kill a process (15 or 9)
r: renice a process with a new priority
q: quit
f/F: delete/add to display
c: command line
i: idle tasks
y: runing tasks


<>: move
x: sort
b+x: bold and reverse
z+x: bold and reverse
H：show threads
R: normal or reverse sort
